---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Log Anomaly Basics - GigaSieve Guide" description="Detect spikes in errors or traffic using hourly grouping.">
    <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-3xl">
        <nav class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">
            <a href="/guides" class="hover:text-cyan-400">Guides</a>
            <span class="mx-2">/</span>
            <span class="text-slate-400">Log Anomaly Basics</span>
        </nav>

        <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-200 mb-4">Log Anomaly Basics</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8">
            Anomaly detection starts with simple baselines. Group logs by hour and compare spikes in 4xx/5xx errors.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 p-6 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-300 mb-4">Signals to watch</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-400 text-sm">
                <li>Sudden 5xx spikes</li>
                <li>Repeated 429 or 403 codes</li>
                <li>Burst traffic from a single IP</li>
                <li>Top URIs changing unexpectedly</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 p-6 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-300 mb-4">How to check quickly</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-400 text-sm">
                <li>Run Status Codes by Hour recipe.</li>
                <li>Compare the top URIs list across hours.</li>
                <li>Inspect the IPs during the spike window.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <a href="/app" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-cyan-500 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg mb-8">
            Try GigaSieve ->
        </a>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-300 mb-4">Related</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <a href="/guides/analyze-nginx-access-log" class="bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-slate-800">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Analyze nginx Access Log</h3>
            </a>
            <a href="/guides/regex-extract-from-log" class="bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-slate-800">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Regex Extract from Log</h3>
            </a>
            <a href="/recipes/logs/status-by-hour" class="bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-slate-800">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Status Codes by Hour</h3>
            </a>
            <a href="/recipes/logs/top-ips" class="bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-slate-800">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Top IPs</h3>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
